interpretation: [An] Leitung von 19. U-Flottille: F.T. [mit Uhrzeitgruppe/Leitnummer] 1224/62 hier gelöst. Verschlüsselt nach RHV [Reservehandverfahren]. Inhalt: [An] UAK von [Loewe? Moewe?] 2: 1315 Uhr Ansteuerungstonne “Fehmarn Südwest”.
translation: [To] Control from 19th Submarine Flotilla: Radiogram [with time group/serial number] 1224/62 solved here. Enciphered according to RHV [Reserve Hand Procedure]. Contents: [To] UAK from [Loewe? Moewe?] 2: [At] 1315 hours [will be at] approach-buoy “Fehmarn Southwest”.
